ome.smuggler.core.msg

Class SourceQueue<M,D>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ome.smuggler.core.msg.SourceQueue<M,D>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChannelSource<ChannelMessage<M,D>>, MessageSource<M,D>

    public class SourceQueue<M,D>
extends java.lang.Object
implements MessageSource<M,D>
    A channel source that queues messages in memory and allows to retrieve the head of the queue to consume messages or do a bulk retrieval of all queued messages.

        public void send(ChannelMessage<M,D> msg)
          throws java.lang.Exception
        Description copied from interface: ChannelSource
        Inputs data into the channel and returns immediately. This is an asynchronous operation, so that the sender never waits for the receiver to get the data.

      • headData
